# ATLAS Guards Directory

This directory contains route guards for ATLAS feature protection.

Guards to be implemented:
- atlas-feature.guard.ts - Checks if ATLAS integration is enabled via feature flag
- atlas-auth.guard.ts - Ensures user is authenticated for ATLAS routes
- atlas-role.guard.ts - Validates user has required roles/permissions

Guards integrate with:
- AtlasConfigService for feature flag checks
- AuthService for authentication validation
- User role/permission system for authorization
